Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是… 叶濑中学的…
