Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是韩国的研究生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是院生？
